  "description": "Lets you keep breaking blocks when you switch items",
  "body": "A simple one-mixin mod that lets you continue breaking a block when you switch items.\n\n## Vanilla\n![A player trying to mine deepslate with wooden and stone pickaxes. Whenever they switch tools, their mining progress resets](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/500faaf91d359778855c5c9a789f58add0ca1bf7.gif)\n\n## Break Free\n![A player mining deepslate with wooden and stone pickaxes. Their mining progress doesn't get reset when switching tools](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/01a621d609d6cbab975775cdd618f5ddc86a653f.gif)\n\n![Stolen by 9Minecraft](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6193fd03429f5ba03b6763c74a0e84bd4cd93c72.png)",
